title: The Lavender Hour: Duncan Trussell & Natasha Leggero: Episode 41
description:
The Lavender Hour: A Weekly Salon-Style Super Show with Duncan Trussell & Natasha Leggero!

Episode 41: Curious Pigs

Duncan discusses the mindset of modern society with Natasha, and later touches on daily habits including video games, reading, and gardening.

Note: This episode costs one dollar, anyone who enjoys The Lavender Hour should be willing to pay this paltry sum.
